###
GET http://localhost:8080/api/chat/debug?question=vacation policy

### Submit feedback (thumbs up)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/chat/feedback
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "responseId": "replace-with-actual-response-id",
  "rating": true,
  "comment": "Very helpful!"
}

### Submit feedback (thumbs down)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/chat/feedback
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "responseId": "replace-with-actual-response-id",
  "rating": false,
  "comment": "Not clear enough"
}

### Get feedback metrics
GET http://localhost:8080/api/chat/metrics
